            {\(\(\(0.000159544134441213`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
                0.00039726622927811566`\ \[ImaginaryI]\), \
\(\(\(0.00016142425164549504`\)\(\[InvisibleSpace]\)\) + 
